data.description: New Roof, New Paint inside and out, New Kitchen, New Flooring!  Step inside and you'll think you're in a new construction home!  This owner has done all the work and now the house just needs to be enjoyed!  Furnish and Decorate to your style!  Seller says if you don't care for the dark green exterior paint, he'll contribute to a repaint.  You're going to love this floor plan.  This property has so many great features starting with the location, Coventry, a No HOA community with well-maintained properties on every street.  This listing is .36 acres and backs up to a large horse pasture.  No rear neighbors!  The backyard is filled with mature landscaping and fruit trees, yet there is a lot of open space for a pool or outbuildings.  When you’re not outside enjoying all this space, then sitting around the fireplace may be just what is needed.  The primary bedroom with its tray ceiling and the ensuite bath with its walk-in tiled shower and a spacious soaking tub are very large and roomy.  The split floor plan is exceptional!  Lots of space inside and outside of this property!  Close to Hwy 326 and Hwy 441. There are shopping centers to the north and the south with grocery stores, restaurants, fast food, etc.  It is a short drive to downtown Ocala where the “Square” has so much to offer.  You’ll love living here!
